s/1.0/modules/content/";a:1:{s:7:"encoded";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:3776:"<p><img class="aligncenter wp-image-5705 size-full" src="http://img.iztwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/seohub.jpg" alt="SEOHub SEO、营销类wordpress主题" width="590" height="300" /></p>\n<p>SEOHub是一套适合SEO、营销推广类网站使用的<span class=''wp_keywordlink''><a href="http://www.iztwp.com/" title="wordpress主题" target="_blank">wordpress主题</a></span>。这套主题设计时尚现代，采用响应式布局，优化了手机端的访问体验，内置兼容多个强大的插件，例如Visual Composer、WPML、WooCommerce、Revolution Slider等，并且通过配合Visual Composer插件及短代码功能可以制作出各种布局元素的页面。SEOHub还支持页面滚动的动画效果，演示数据也可以通过后台直接一键导入。</p>\n<p><img class="aligncenter wp-image-5706 size-full" src="http://img.iztwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/SEOHub-desc.jpg" alt="SEOHub SEO、营销类wordpress主题" width="616" height="3569" /></p>\n<h3 id="item-description__key-features">主题介绍</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Simple and Functional design</li>\n<li>Easy to install, run and update!</li>\n<li>Modern, Flexible, Customizable!</li>\n<li>WordPress 4.0+ Tested and Approved!</li>\n<li>Built with valid HTML5 and CSS3 code</li>\n<li>Cross-Browser Compatibility: FireFox, Safari, Chrome, IE9+</li>\n<li>One-Click demo install</li>\n<li><strong>Layout Features</strong>:\n<ul>\n<li>Boxed and Wide pages layouts</li>\n<li>Visual Composer support – create unlimited variants of Homepage Layouts</li>\n<li>Different Header Styles</li>\n<li>Enable/Disable Multi-Functional User Panel</li>\n<li>Many awesome Hover Effects</li>\n<li>Fully Responsive Layout</li>\n<li>Enable/Disable Retina Option</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><strong>Slider Options</strong>:\n<ul>\n<li>Includes Swiper Slider for posts and galleries</li>\n<li>Includes Revolution Slider as Home slider</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><strong>Navigation Options</strong>:\n<ul>\n<li>User menu and Main menu support</li>\n<li>Main menu slider</li>\n<li>Awesome CSS3/jQuery animation effects</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><strong>Powerful Framework</strong>:\n<ul>\n<li>Setting Inheritance and Override System</li>\n<li>Shortcode Builder</