8553:"<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-5633" src="http://img.iztwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/Symetrio.png" alt="Symetrio 运动健身类Wordpress主题" width="590" height="303" /></p>\n<p>Symetrio是一套来自<span class=''wp_keywordlink''><a href="http://www.iztwp.com/go/?r=aHR0cDovL3RoZW1lZm9yZXN0Lm5ldC9jYXRlZ29yeS93b3JkcHJlc3M/cmVmPXdoeXVu" title="themeforest" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">themeforest</a></span>的运动健身类<span class=''wp_keywordlink''><a href="http://www.iztwp.com/tag/business-theme" title="wordpress企业主题" target="_blank">wordpress企业主题</a></span>。这套主题非常简洁大方，在<span class=''wp_keywordlink''><a href="http://www.iztwp.com/go/?r=aHR0cDovL3RoZW1lZm9yZXN0Lm5ldC9jYXRlZ29yeS93b3JkcHJlc3M/cmVmPXdoeXVu" title="themeforest" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">themeforest</a></span>网站运动健身同类主题里面销量第一。Symetrio 支持多种首页风格，具体每种风格的效果可以查看演示链接。Symetrio 主题还可以配合WooCommerce插件实现商城功能，配合bbPress支持社区交流功能。</p>\n<h3>主题介绍</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Powerfull Schedule module – create simple module and advanced schedules. Use prdefined modules</li>\n<li>Multi place location – Symetrio supports multiple clubs locations. You can narrow trainers set / activities / rooms form by assigning them a specific location</li>\n<li>Event module</li>\n<li>One Page template</li>\n<li>PayPal payment integration</li>\n<li>Cross-Browser Compatibility: FireFox, Safari, Chrome, IE9, IE10, IE11</li>\n<li>Sticky header – You can decide about header menu visibility</li>\n<li>Smart – Menu</li>\n<li>Full width &amp; Boxed mode</li>\n<li>Fancy mobile menu</li>\n<li>Standard &amp; Mega Menu</li>\n<li>Paralax Background</li>\n<li>2 totaly different blog styles</li>\n<li>Video Background (You can use a local video / stream from YouTube or Vimeo)</li>\n<li>Free &amp; outstanding support for customers\n<ul>\n<li>Full Online Documentation</li>\n<li>FREE Lifetime Updates – get all the new features we add in each future update for free</li>\n<li>We take pride in offering THE BEST after sales support around. We care about your site as much as you do, and we will help in any possible way</li>\n<li>Multiple HD video tutorials for easy instruction</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><b>Included 40 CSS3 animations</b></li>\n<li>Awesome Wonster Slider</li>\n<li>Instagram Integration</li>\n<li>Mega backgorund – animated background ( from selected photos ) on your page.</li>\n<li>WordPress Multi-Site (WPMU) – Tested and Approved</li>\n<li><b>Unlimited colors element – Change theme colors using built-in WordPress Customization panel</b></li>\n<li>Social media integration</li>\n<li>Amazing Google Maps Builder\n<ul>\n<li>The mechanism for creating paths and tracks</li>\n<li>Street view</li>\n<li>Unlimited number of pins on your map</li>\n<li>Your own, custom map pin</li>\n<li>70 predefined map styles</li>\n<li>100 predefined map pins</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>3 Different Blog Layouts</li>\n<li>4 Headers, 6 Fotters</li>\n<li>Build your site in a simple way. Build your site in a simple way. You get probably the best shortcode mechanism throughout the whole Evanto. Create unlimited layouts, chose from over 60 difrent type of shortcodes. Create layouts with no limitations.\n<ul>\n<li>48 functional shortcodes</li>\n<li>12 fitness – shortcodes\n<ul>\n<li>Class – allows you to display specific classes, available 2 forms of presentation</li>\n<li>Classes – allows you to crate lists with classes, available filtering after, category and  gym location, available 2 forms of presentation</li>\n<li>Class schedule – wit static / multi week module</li>\n<li>Daily schedule – classes for specific day in condensed form</li>\n<li>Event – allows you to display specific event</li>\n<li>Events – allows you to crate lists with events, available filtering after, category and  gym location, available 2 forms of presentation</li>\n<li>Open hours – dedicated element allows you to display open hours in your club</li>\n<li>Pass –  dedicated element allows you to display specific club pass</li>\n<li>Passes – allows you to crate lists with passes, available filtering after, category and  gym location</li>\n<li>Rooms – allows you to crate lists with rooms, available filtering after, category and  gym location</li>\n<li>Trainer – allows you to display specific trainer, available 2 forms of presentation</li>\n<li>Trainers – allows you to crate lists with trainers, available filtering after, category, gym location, specializations, trainers functions, available 2 forms of presentation</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>Amazing Wonster Options\n<ul>\n<li>Change color for each element you see</li>\n<li>Turn on/off responsive version by one click</li>\n<li>Turn on/off Boxed style</li>\n<li>Change phone &amp; email in header withing seconds</li>\n<li>Choose between different layouts with one click</li>\n<li>Use built-in SEO fields</li>\n<li>Unlimited sidebars</li>\n<li>Choose fonts for each text on page (you can use Latin, Cyrilic and many other types of font)</li>\n<li>Built-in translator (translate anything you want on page with our built-in translator)</li>\n<li>Choose between backgrounds images, colors, etc.</li>\n<li>Upload logo &amp; favicon in few seconds</li>\n<li>Retina Ready</li>\n<li>Blog options support</li>\n<li>Portfolio options support</li>\n<li>Custom CSS support</li>\n<li>and much more</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>New Page Options – For each side there is a number of interesting options to help you affect appearance of the page\n<ul>\n<li>Page menu – allows you to set a different menu on each page</li>\n<li>Enable clean menu mode</li>\n<li>Enable transparent mode</li>\n<li>Show/hide breadcumbs</li>\n<li>Sidebar position – Decide about the visibility of the sidebar and its position. For each page, you can assign different sidebar.</li>\n<li>Custom css – You can make quick modifications to the appearance of each page by adding your own CSS code.</li>\n<li>Header settings</li>\n<li>Footer Settings</li>\n<li>SEO – manage seo fields for each page.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>Advanced Blog Options\n<ul>\n<li>Number of