</span>主要针对健康食品、农业等相关行业设计的，所以页面也采用了非常清新的绿色。主题支持6种首页布局、产品（PORTFOLIO）、博客和商场等功能，支持自适应，以及热门的一些插件（Visual Composer、Revolution Slider等），似的主题功能更加强大。</p>\n<h3 id="item-description__key-features">主题介绍</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Modern, Flexible, Clean!</li>\n<li>WordPress 4+ Tested and Approved!</li>\n<li>Built with HTML5 and CSS3</li>\n<li>Cross-Browser Compatibility: FireFox, Safari, Chrome, IE9+</li>\n<li>One-Click demo install</li>\n<li>Child theme support</li>\n<li><strong>Layout Features</strong>:\n<ul>\n<li>6 Homepage Layouts</li>\n<li>2 Menu Styles</li>\n<li>Enable/Disable Multi-Functional User Panel</li>\n<li>2 Footer Styles</li>\n<li>3 Blog Styles</li>\n<li>Fully Responsive Layout</li>\n<li>Enable/Disable Retina Option</li>\n<li><strong>Slider Options</strong>:\n<ul>\n<li>Includes Revolution Slider</li>\n<li>Post Slider</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><strong>Navigation Options</strong>:\n<ul>\n<li>3 Menu Types: Standard Upper Menu, Double Menu, Hide Menu</li>\n<li>Drop-down menu</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><strong>ThemeRex Framework</strong>:\n<ul>\n<li>Setting Inheritance and Override System</li>\n<li>Shortcode Builder</li>\n<li>Visual Composer</li>\n<li>Custom Theme Options Panel</li>\n<li>Media Content Manager</li>\n<li>&#8230;and many more!</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><strong>Translation Options</strong>:\n<ul>\n<li>Localized: .po &amp; .mo files included</li>\n<li>PO Composer: working with .po and .mo files has now become much easier!</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><strong>Plugins Compatibility</strong>:\n<ul>\n<li>Revolution Slider</li>\n<li>Visual Composer</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><strong>ThemeRex Widgets Set</strong>:\n<ul>\n<li>Flickr</li>\n<li>Twitter</li>\n<li>Instagram</li>\n<li>Popular Posts</li>\n<li>Recent Posts</li>\n<li>Recent Reviews</li>\n<li>Top 10</li>\n<li>Advertisement</li>\n<li>Logo</li>\n<li>Social Icons</li>\n<li>ThemeRex Shortcodes:</li>\n<li>Blogger</li>\n<li>Content Slider</li>\n<li>Skills</li>\n<li>QR-cod</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><strong>ThemeRex Shortcodes</strong>:\n<ul>\n<li>Blogger</li>\n<li>Lense</li>\n<li>Content Slider</li>\n<li>Video List</li>\n<li>Skills</li>\n<li>eMailer</li>\n<li>Timeline</li>\n<li>Scroller</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>A lot of <strong>Shortcodes</strong> included:\n<ul>\n<li>Accordion</li>\n<li>Button</li>\n<li>Columns</li>\n<li>Google Map</li>\n<li>Hide</li>\n<li>Highlight</li>\n<li>Section</li>\n<li>Table</li>\n<li>Tabs</li>\n<li>Team</li>\n<li>Testimonials</li>\n<li>Title</li>\n<li>Tooltip</li>\n<li>Toggle</li>\n<li>and more …</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><strong>SEO Ready</strong>:\n<ul>\n<li>HTML code integrated into the theme meets the best SEO approaches</li>\n<li>The theme support compatibility with “All on One SEO Pack” &amp; “SEO by Yoast”</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>Save money with <strong>Included Plugins</strong>:\n<ul>\n<li>Revolution Slider – $19</li>\n<li>Visual Composer – $30</li>\n<li>PO Composer – $16</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>Performance Optimization</li>\n<li>Two variants of icon display: Fontella Icon set and Images Icons</li>\n<li>Google web fonts</li>\n<li>Great Professional Support</li>\n<li>Documentation included</li>\n<li>Regular Updates</li>\n<li>And many more that we might have forgotten to mention…</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a:1:{s:10:"commentRss";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:49:"http://www.iztwp.com/theme/healthy-farm.html/feed";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:38:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/";a:1:{s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:1:"0";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}}}s:27:"http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom";a:1:{s:4:"link";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:0:"";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:3:{s:4:"href";s:25:"http://www.iztwp.com/feed";s:3:"rel";s:4:"self";s:4:"type";s:19:"application/rss+xml";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0